==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Coluber
<hw>Col"u*ber</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L., a
serpent.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A genus of harmless
serpents.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><note>⟦hand⟧ Linn⟦ae⟧us placed in this genus all serpents, whether
venomous or not, whose scales beneath the tail are arranged in pairs;
but by modern writers it is greatly restricted.</note>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>colubrid</ent>⟦br⟧
